{"tid":922664,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日係紀念日，今日係佢生日","createTime":"2018-11-30T14:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T20:38:05.000Z","uid":210071,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3c9ce4e60254b62b38b722f905aad93d83ced97e","tid":922664,"uid":210071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:41:34.000Z","msg":"話說我明知佢今日唔得閒 要返學又要補習，亦令我有時間去同班中同去聯誼下打下波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n所以琴日一早將啲禮物一次過送哂比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n之後今晚就去打波，諗住一打完有時間就狗衝去見女朋友撞正佢補完習。<br />\n<br />\n點知我Miss左佢個call，心知不妙都即刻打俾佢，佢又唔聽電話又唔覆wts<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n終於，佢覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但係一幅影住地下嘅圖話佢係個度，之後叫我搵佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好啦經過差唔多15分鐘嘅尋寶我終於搵到佢。<br />\n<br />\n但已經哄唔掂，話好多project要做要返屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我屌，應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n幅圖係咁樣：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Knz1Ku7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnz1Ku7.jpg&h=dbd573ca&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1568d9464207ded60f3c411cc25dcc43dc53be6","tid":922664,"uid":7452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T14:42:23.000Z","msg":"係我屋企"},{"pid":"b30da1f5127822b4482d4838dd7606037d59d163","tid":922664,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T20:38:05.000Z","msg":"生日快樂"}]}